%p These are all the trips I'm signed up for
- if @my_registrations.empty?
  %p You haven't signed up for any events yet. Click on the link at the top called 'HB Trip Listings' to find a trip you may be interested in
- else
  %table

    %tr
      %th Start
      %th End
      %th Event
      %th My Status
      %th Event Status
    - @my_registrations.each do |f|
      %tr
        %td= f.event.start_date.pretty
        %td= f.event.end_date.pretty
        %td= link_to f.event.event_name, event_path(:id => f.event_id)
        %td= f.register_status
        %td= f.event.event_status
